00:27:50,000 --> 00:27:54,200
He really doesn't have a bit of merit? Not even a little bit?

496
00:27:54,200 --> 00:27:55,800
Merit?

497
00:27:55,800 --> 00:27:57,400
I'll reluctantly...

498
00:27:57,400 --> 00:28:02,000
say that he can be considered handsome.

499
00:28:02,000 --> 00:28:04,000
As for his physique,

500
00:28:05,000 --> 00:28:08,400
it's fine, but, of course, not as good as yours.

501
00:28:08,400 --> 00:28:10,600
You m-must not misunderstand.

502
00:28:10,600 --> 00:28:14,400
I am not one of those shallow girls who is only attracted by appearance.

503
00:28:14,400 --> 00:28:17,360
I just think that Third Young Master Mei

504
00:28:17,360 --> 00:28:20,200
looks quite handsome when he saves people.

505
00:28:23,500 --> 00:28:25,400
But it's just...

506
00:28:26,600 --> 00:28:30,600
he really doesn't know how to express his feelings.

507
00:28:30,600 --> 00:28:35,400
Also, he always pushes everyone so far away; he's like an iceberg.

508
00:28:35,400 --> 00:28:37,700
Let's not talk about this. Night-Spirited Hero,

509
00:28:37,700 --> 00:28:43,200
